---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 556
  - Title: Amitâyur-Dhyâna-Sûtra
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Grace=Liberty
  - 583
---
It is by the power of Buddha only that one can see that pure land (of
Buddha) as clear as one sees the image of one's face reflected in the
transparent mirror held up before one.
